de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.pairs

Class Pair<FIRST,SECOND>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.utilities.pairs.Pair<FIRST,SECOND>
  • Type Parameters:
    FIRST - first type
    SECOND - second type
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SpatialPair

    public class Pair<FIRST,SECOND>
extends Object
    Simple class wrapping two objects. Do not use this for primitive types such as Integer and Double - avoid the memory waste and garbage collection overhead! Does not implement any "special" interfaces such as Comparable. If you need more complicated pairs, please use domain specific code, with more meaningful field names and comparators.
    Author:
    Erich Schubert
